nl.vpro.util

Interface CountedIterator<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, CloseableIterator<T>, Iterator<T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    CountedPeekingIterator<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicWrappedIterator, CallbackIterator, ElasticSearchIterator, ElasticSearchIterator, JsonArrayIterator, MergedSortedIterator, TailAdder, WrappedIterator

    public interface CountedIterator<T>
extends Iterator<T>, CloseableIterator<T>
    An iterator that is also aware of the current position getCount(), and optionally of the size of the object that is iterated getSize(), and also optionally of a 'total' size (in case this iterator presents some sub-collection) getTotalSize().
    Since:
    0.31
    Author:
    Michiel Meeuwissen
